001 Login page (https://aqa-complexapp.onrender.com/)

Username field //input[@id='username-register']
Email field //input[@id='email-register']
Password field //input[@id='password-register']
Sign button //button[@type='submit']
Sign In button //button[text()='Sign In']


002 Main page (after login) (https://aqa-complexapp.onrender.com/)

Sign out button //button[text()='Sign Out']
Create post button //a[@href='/create-post']
My profile button //a[@class='mr-2']


003 Create post page (https://aqa-complexapp.onrender.com/create-post)

Title field //input[@id='post-title']
Body Content field //textarea[@id='post-body']
Check box //input[@name='uniquePost']
Select value //option[@value='All Users']
Save New Post button //button[text()='Save New Post']


004 Success post creation page (https://aqa-complexapp.onrender.com/post/<id>)

//div[text()='New post successfully created.']
//*/u[contains(text(),'All Users')]
