005 Profile page (https://aqa-complexapp.onrender.com/profile/<username>)

Exist post //a[@class='list-group-item list-group-item-action']
Following button //div[text()='Following']
Stop following button //button[text()='Stop Following ']


006 Post page (https://aqa-complexapp.onrender.com/post/<id>)

Edit button //a[@class='text-primary mr-2']


007 Edit post page (https://aqa-complexapp.onrender.com/post/<id>/edit)

Title field //input[@id='post-title']
Is this post unique check box //input[@name='uniquePost']
Select value //option[@value='All Users']
Save Updates button //button[text()='Save Updates']


